column3: Premature until the softfork is accepted, no?\n
(Also, much prefer CHECKMATURITYVERIFY for a name...)\n
I also think this is too early. Until the softfork goes through this is still effectively a NOP.\n
are we going to do this in 0.13.0?\n
@laanwj This will not cleanly cherry-pick to 0.12, would you like be to create the backport for 0.12 as a separate PR?\n
@btcdrak Yes, I think a separate backport PR would make sense in this case, as it's probably easier to  do the replacement another time than try to coax git into cherry-picking this.\n
